# Wargroove, with Flydigi Apex 2 in mind
JoyXY WASD deadzone 40 # Move camera
CamXY Mouse 100 # Move Cursor
TriggerR M1 # Select
BumperR M2 # Move
BumperL Shift # Queue all the things

MenuL Tab
MenuR Escape # Main Menu

DpadXY arrows # Move cursor?

ActionB M2 # Cancel / Unit Stats
ActionA Enter # Confirm
